abstract: >
  Mercury MCP exposes a 23-LLM cross-architecture observation database to any
  agent that speaks the Model Context Protocol. Built entirely on consumer
  hardware (Mac mini + NVIDIA DGX Spark) at near-zero compute cost. Provides
  per-model anchor dimension data, per-layer functional fingerprints, and
  cross-architecture layer alignment matrices for 13 distinct LLM families.
